### Basic Usage

- New Post
  - bundle exec rake new_post["title"]
  
- New Page
  - bundle exec rake new_page[title/index.markdown] 
  
- Optimize images (now performed inline as part of 'generate')
  - bundle exec rake optimize images

- Generate site
  - bundle exec rake generate

- Deploy site
  - bundle exec rake deploy
  
- Notify search engines of updates
  - bundle exec rake notify

- Push source
 - git add .
 - git commit -m 'DESCRIPTION'
 - git push origin source